('29698', '706', 'Independent Green-Crewed Maelstrom', 'With the Maelstrom, versatility is the name of the game. Its defensive capabilities make it ideally suited for small raid groups or solo work, while its 8 turret hardpoints present opportunities for untold carnage on the fleet battlefield.\r\n\r\nThe markings on this ship reveal no obvious connection to the Republic.', '', '19000000', '19000000', '120', '1', '2', '0', '0'),
