('29787', '705', 'Independent Green-Crewed Bellicose', 'Being a highly versatile class of Minmatar ships, the Bellicose has been used as a combat juggernaut as well as a support ship for wings of frigates. While not quite in the league of newer navy cruisers, the Bellicose is still a very solid ship for most purposes, especially in terms of long range combat.\r\n\r\nThe markings on this ship reveal no obvious connection to the Republic.', '', '9900000', '99000', '120', '1', '2', '0', '0'),
('29788', '705', 'Independent Green-Crewed Rupture', 'The Rupture is slow for a Minmatar ship, but it more than makes up for it in power. The Rupture has superior firepower and is used by the Minmatar Republic both to defend space stations and other stationary objects and as part of massive attack formations.\r\n\r\nThe markings on this ship reveal no obvious connection to the Republic.', '', '9900000', '99000', '120', '1', '2', '0', '0'),
