('30842', '31', 'Interbus Shuttle', 'Interbus commissioned Duvolle Laboratories to design them an upgraded shuttlecraft in YC 106. The result was this vessel, which combines compact size with a surprisingly large cargo hold - ideal for the multipurpose transportation that Interbus specializes in.\r\n\r\nThe ship remained a closely-guarded Interbus asset for many years, but in YC111 it was made available to select capsuleer pilots as part of an outreach programme intended to raise awareness of the Interbus brand among the growing capsuleer population. It remains, however, a very rare sight among the spacelanes and is considered by many to be a valuable collector''s item.', '', '1600000', '5000', '20', '1', '8', '5000', '1618'),
