('32367', '306', 'Training Container - Archeology', 'This container must be accessed using a <b>Civilian Analyzer</b>. As soon as a successful salvage attempt is detected, it will unlock. Inside, the <b>“Proof of Discovery: Magnetometric”</b> document can be retrieved.\r\n\r\nIf at first the container appears empty, please wait a few minutes for a new document to be provided.', '26_11', '10000', '27500', '2700', '1', '0', '0', '0'),
