('32442', '1019', 'Mjolnir Citadel Cruise Missile', 'Citadel Cruise Missiles are designed for long range bombardment of capital ships and installations. They are a specialized design usable only by capital ships.\r\n\r\nNothing more than a baby nuclear warhead, this guided missile wreaks havoc with the delicate electronic systems aboard a starship. Specifically designed to damage shield systems, it is able to ravage heavily shielded targets in no time.', '20_16', '1500', '0.3', '0', '100', '0', '350000', '1287'),
