('32455', '927', 'Ishukone Hauler', 'Industrials are a common sight in the universe of EVE, connecting supply points to each other. Convoys usually have armed escorts, so attacking them is risky.', '', '13500000', '270000', '5250', '1', '1', '0', '0'),
('32456', '701', 'Mordus Escort', 'Contracted for security purposes, Mordu''s Legion sent this escort in order to protect the interests of Ishukone in the Intaki system. This ship is on sentry duty. Though it has orders to allow traffic through the system, it will fight back if provoked.', '', '9600000', '96000', '450', '1', '1', '0', '0'),
('32457', '1006', 'Ishukone Escort', 'Ishukone has sent part of its internal security force to protect the corporation''s interests in the Intaki system. The megacorporation purchased the system during Tibus Heth''s blind auction.', '', '10100000', '101000', '235', '1', '1', '0', '0'),
('32458', '1012', 'Infrastructure Hub', 'An Infrastructure Hub is the cornerstone of any empire´s expansion into nullsec territory.\r\n\r\nOnce online, it allows the owner to cultivate the system it is placed in by applying one of the upgrades available. These upgrades range from simple improvements to a system´s financial infrastructure, to defensive upgrades giving the system owner significant advantages.\r\n\r\nAs an added bonus, the Infrastructure Hub functions as a defensive structure as well, as sovereignty cannot be taken while it is still online.', '', '1000000', '750000', '10000', '1', '0', '500000000', '1275'),
('32459', '52', 'Civilian Warp Disruptor', 'Warp Disruptors are used to disrupt a target ship''s navigation computer, which prevents it from warping.<br><br>These specially-designed Civilian variants are not strong enough to be used in live combat and are sufficient for instructional purposes only. ', '04_09', '0', '5', '0', '1', '0', '39424', '0'),
('32461', '509', 'Civilian Light Missile Launcher', 'Favored by many for its average capacity and firing rate. Useful in both fast attack raids and longer battles.\r\n', '12_12', '0', '5', '0.6', '1', '0', '6000', '0'),
('32463', '384', 'Civilian Scourge Light Missile', 'From its humble beginnings in tiny Minmatar design labs, the Scourge light missile has quickly established itself throughout the star cluster as a premier missile for light launchers.\r\n', '13_04', '700', '0.015', '0', '100', '0', '500', '0'),
