('32811', '28', 'Iteron Mark IV Amastris Edition', 'The Iteron Mark IV Amastris Edition is a limited edition cargo hauler awarded to pilots who have displayed extraordinary aptitude in capsuleer training. \r\n\r\nIt boasts a more powerful warp engine and a bigger cargo hold than its standard Class-IV counterpart, in addition to state-of-the-art lateral thrusters allowing for improved agility. Among recent capsuleer graduates from New Eden''s academic institutions, this vessel is considered a distinguished status symbol.\r\n\r\nGallente Industrial Skill Bonus: 5% Bonus Cargo Capacity and Max Velocity per skill level', '', '11250000', '265000', '5250', '1', '8', '600000', '1614'),
